ake visits more convenient than staying in a hotel or motel. Of course, trashing hotels is half the fun of touring, but you’ll have to pick up the tab.\\n\\n**Game Features**\\n\\n* Explore a musical open-world environment.\\n* Find other musicians to form a band.\\n* Hire managers to find recording contracts, endorsements, book individual gigs or entire tours.\\n* Fully customize your band’s appearance and van with thousands of combinations of hairstyles, makeup, clothing and paint jobs.\\n* Purchase a variety of houses and apartments to call home, with hundreds of customization options.\\n* Live the classic rockstar life by trashing hotels & motels for inspiration and fun.\\n* Choose from 600 different types of real equipment to see what works best for your band.\\n* Booking venues and tours across more than 130 cities in the United States.\\n* Take on 40 side jobs to earn cash while working your way up to stardom.\\n* Explores thousands of locations including bars, theaters, stadiums, clothing stores, recording studios, photography studios, hotels, art galleries, print shops, parks, cemeteries, and more.\\n\\n**Backwards Compatibility**\\n\\nThis repack IS NOT backwards compatible with my previous RS2 repacks.\\n\\n[2D](https://fitgirl-repacks.site/tag/2d/) [3D](https://fitgirl-repacks.site/tag/3d/) [Lifestyle](https://fitgirl-repacks.site/tag/lifestyle/) [Managerial](https://fitgirl-repacks.site/tag/managerial/)\\n\\n| |If you like what I do, please consider donating to help me maintain this site, compressing RDP and seedboxes for my repacks. |[Donate to FitGirl](http://fitgirl-repacks.site/donations/) |\\n| --- | --- | --- |\\n\\n[Lossless Repack](https://fitgirl-repacks.site/category/lossless-repack/)\\n\\n# [Space Hulk: Ultimate Pack – v1.5.1a + 6 DLCs](https://fitgirl-repacks.site/space-hulk/)\\n\\n[20/06/2026](https://fitgirl-repacks.\\n\\n...\\n\\nsite/page/771/) [Next →](https://fitgirl-repacks.site/page/2/)\\n\\n## The ONLY official site for FitGirl Repa