    {
      "type": "thought",
      "text": "I found the issue! The WSL service \"LxssManager\" is in \"StopPending\" status, which means it's trying to stop but hasn't completed yet. This is likely why all the WSL commands are timing out - the service is not properly running.\n\nLet me try to restart the WSL service to fix this issue.",
