      "text": "The WSL service is stuck in \"StopPending\" state, which means it's trying to stop but can't complete. This is why all WSL commands are timing out. I need to find a way to properly restart the WSL service.\n\nLet me try to use taskkill to kill any WSL-related processes and then restart the service.",
