    {
      "type": "thought",
      "text": "The WSL service is stuck in \"StopPending\" state. This is a common issue that can happen when WSL processes are not properly terminated or when there's a system issue. Let me try to restart the WSL service properly by first stopping it completely and then starting it again.",
